title: Looking To Coach Lower Elo Players
body:
Hey,

Wasn't sure where to post this so i just put it in this section of the forum, basically i want try and see if i can get into a bit of coaching, in result i would need some people to coach. I want to focus on lower elo type of players who are willing to listen and sorta have an open mind.

I generally only teach ADC as its my main role, regardless feel free to add me in game :) 

Thanks! 
{{champion:67}}
